{"tid":2014337,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場報案中心警員疑私吞失物 被控盜竊明天提堂","createTime":"2020-05-13T03:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T09:49:50.000Z","uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3e3f8e6eeece0a760c62243f08a5a9f4509038cb","tid":2014337,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T03:24:22.000Z","msg":"機場客運大樓報案中心去年發生懷疑警員監守自盜案件，事件經過一年零三個月後，26歲姓馮警員今日被控以一項「盜竊」罪，案件將於明日（13日）在沙田裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n事件發生於去年2月13日，一名31歲姓楊女子在機場拾獲一個內有約5萬元現金的銀包，之後交到機場客運大樓的報案中心，由當值警務人員處理有關失物，惟1個多小時後物主到報案中心報失及認領，揭發當值警員並未立案，懷疑有人監守自盜，警方其後調查以涉嫌「盜竊」拘捕一名26歲姓馮警員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200512/64ZWPS65MJMJ6MVDVEOJUVRIBI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200512%2F64ZWPS65MJMJ6MVDVEOJUVRIBI%2F&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NXdT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=56da15d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200512%2F64ZWPS65MJMJ6MVDVEOJUVRIBI%2F&h=df6937a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200512/64ZWPS65MJMJ6MVDVEOJUVRIBI/</a>"},{"pid":"937a41a498c4c7b958ce34bc5d4ca619c8de1ff7","tid":2014337,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T03:28:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://d2i91erehhsxi2.cloudfront.net/appledaily/2020/05/12/5ebadb5ad60180000720ec92/20200512_ccm_07_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2i91erehhsxi2.cloudfront.net%2Fappledaily%2F2020%2F05%2F12%2F5ebadb5ad60180000720ec92%2F20200512_ccm_07_w.mp4&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NXdT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=dc147707\" target=\"_blank\">https://d2i91erehhsxi2.cloudfront.net/appledaily/2020/05/12/5ebadb5ad60180000720ec92/20200512_ccm_07_w.mp4</a>"},{"pid":"4a340b933b530002af383b0a081a2404c04fcb49","tid":2014337,"uid":294481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T03:29:58.000Z","msg":"係唔係應該去助慶"},{"pid":"4fd2ff81d973e83ae2